##############################################################
# MiniJava/UP library for MIPS/Spim -- version that assumes
#    one-word boolean on stack
# author: Steven R. Vegdahl
# date: 7-13 July 2004
# modified 12-17 March 2007
# modified 3-25 May 2007
# modified 2 May 2015
# modified 7 March 2016
